{"tid":172282,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"千萬不要在床上放屁","createTime":"2017-03-25T20:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T05:12:22.000Z","uid":37240,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe42e3ac4bc923eb2738caa7c840c4624c08f89c","tid":172282,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T20:16:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我有個習慣係走個枕頭，坐係床頭用電腦<br />\n岩岩唔知做乜鬼好多屁放，仲要係臭到仆街個隻<br />\n咁我有屁就放啦，中間都有離開張床去屙尿呀飲水咁<br />\n咁就loop左幾次，過左差唔多一個鐘啦<br />\n而家準備訓教，發現d屁滲左入床褥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有陣揮之不去既臭味，每捽一下個床褥，就有一道濃郁榴連咁既屁味揮發出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n捽極都捽唔哂，訓係張床慘過食屎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問下有咩解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce6dd9d06f88ae4851177e7379bef9fda3f10cf","tid":172282,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T20:17:41.000Z","msg":"好爽喎 一咯自己啲屁味一路打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46860c03d0cefd622df05be8cf3f76b79e170ba4","tid":172282,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T20:21:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好爽喎 一咯自己啲屁味一路打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我想訓教，而家塊面食正d臭屁，陰d陰d咁散發出黎"},{"pid":"86adf28a23e72a01d0063b94a90e950ac46941c2","tid":172282,"uid":53462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T20:22:32.000Z","msg":"其實你賴左屎."},{"pid":"943be69823e8b130c1ab25a3b2e8fb9cf638cac2","tid":172282,"uid":5574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T20:24:19.000Z","msg":"上返三注香就得架啦"},{"pid":"152ca93172608e78947849083316335a291c8099","tid":172282,"uid":81220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T20:35:43.000Z","msg":"搵風筒吹啲屁味出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d2e6c7826722b99efe1267f518d80618bd1d67","tid":172282,"uid":47674,"like":